SIMPLE: ebon
RECORDS: 2

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Ebon
<hw>Eb"on</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Consisting
of ebony.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Like ebony, especially in color; black;
dark.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Night, sable goddess! from her <qex>ebon</qex> throne.</q>
<rj><qau>Young.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ebon</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Ebon
<hw>Eb"on</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Ebony.</def> <mark>[Poetic]</mark>
⟦ldquo⟧Framed of <xex>ebon</xex> and ivory.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Sir W.
Scott.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ebonist</ent>⟦br⟧
